{"tid":784773,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得香港人質素愈來愈差","createTime":"2018-08-18T15:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T04:45:46.000Z","uid":95565,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4801d75f87a550e8efa3d29b3e8663134f80eae","tid":784773,"uid":95565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"返工無可能識到真朋友，個個利益行先，見高就抬見低就踩，或者夠蠢自願俾佢地利用，又或者要夠奸同佢地同流合污，要識講是非先代表識social，真係理性討論就俾人嫌悶嫌老土，所有野要夠平夠快，一般所謂嘅速食文化。<br />\n<br />\n連港豬、師奶、廢老都識蝦毒撚，你地嘅善良只係佢地眼中嘅廢柴，跟住班MK個個扮毒撚食晒d女玩到中出即飛留返俾真毒撚埋單<br />\n<br />\n呢個CLS社會，有冇可能差到盡頭便物極必反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970cabb0a8d450faca203699b2876b164c32910c","tid":784773,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲都自私勢利"},{"pid":"c5ab27160ac570d86e157675b6ea806b1ea0a0ee","tid":784773,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"同途<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596f37002086f4a7e9129e6fba4f12fb9fbf5aae","tid":784773,"uid":180538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"第一日係香港啊？<br />\n<br />\n認命lo<br />\n<br />\n唔認命就努力改變佢<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得囡比mk仔食曬<br />\n<br />\n事實係自己都唔識囡<br />\n<br />\n連囡都唔識 點知佢地比mk仔食曬<br />\n<br />\n香港係差 差在d人 唔單止係mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed8adbbe81185fd2b4901e542e907aa59d15cbd","tid":784773,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"香港人一直以來都係利字當頭，以前係，而家都係。"},{"pid":"343ddaedac7b9127fb22ff8e6f8be6eb10d29e7b","tid":784773,"uid":95565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"